5. 🧠 시스템 아키텍처 한눈에 보기
Browser
  └─ Frontend (Phaser + TypeScript + Vite)
      ├─ Static assets (/)
      └─ API requests (/api)
             ↓
         Nginx Ingress
             ├─ PROD frontend live
             ├─ STG frontend live
             ├─ /api -> Spring Boot backend
             ├─ auth.ssafymaker.cloud -> Keycloak
             ├─ jenkins.ssafymaker.cloud -> Jenkins
             └─ n8n.ssafymaker.cloud -> n8n
                     ↓
                Spring Boot Backend
                  ├─ Auth / Session(BFF)
                  ├─ Save File / Inventory
                  ├─ Challenge
                  ├─ Death Dashboard
                  └─ Asset Manifest
                     ↓
          PostgreSQL / Redis / RabbitMQ
